name: Millionaire Out Of Nowhere
description: Millionaire Out Of Nowhere is a community-run meme coin for the dreamers, the degens, and the lucky lunatics. Our message is, all you have to do is hold. We want to bring back the culture of holding coins because you believe in something, join the community and hang out with people that have a common goal. It is every meme coin traders dream to become a millionaire out of nowhere and we are creating the brand that vibes with that.
